' SD-01. UC-001 장애물이 없을 때 직진 청소
' Related Use Case: UC-001. 장애물이 없을 때 직진 청소
' Intent: 전방 장애물이 없을 때 일반 청소 출력과 전진 명령을 생성하는 내부 객체 협력을 표현한다.
' Note: 전방 장애물 또는 먼지 감지 시 각각 UC-002, UC-006으로 전환되는 대안 흐름을 포함한다.

@startuml SD_01_UC001_Forward_Cleaning
title SD-01 - UC-001 장애물이 없을 때 직진 청소

actor "센서 입력" as Sensor
participant "RVC SW Controller" as Controller
participant "SensorState" as SensorState
participant "AutomaticCleaning" as Cleaning
participant "CleaningPolicy" as Policy
participant "CleaningCommand" as CleaningCommand
participant "MovementCommand" as MovementCommand
actor "청소 장치" as Cleaner
actor "주행 장치" as Drive

Sensor -> Controller: reportFrontObstacleState(frontObstacleDetected=false)
activate Controller
Controller -> SensorState: updateFrontObstacle(frontObstacleDetected=false)
Controller -> Cleaning: handleSensorState(SensorState)
activate Cleaning
Cleaning -> SensorState: isFrontObstacleDetected()
SensorState --> Cleaning: false
Cleaning -> Policy: normalPowerLevel()
Policy --> Cleaning: NORMAL
Cleaning -> CleaningCommand: create(NORMAL)
CleaningCommand --> Cleaning: cleaningCommand
Cleaning -> Cleaner: setCleaningPower(NORMAL)
Cleaning -> MovementCommand: create(MOVE_FORWARD)
MovementCommand --> Cleaning: movementCommand
Cleaning -> Drive: moveForward()
Cleaning -> Cleaning: keepStatus(CLEANING)
Cleaning --> Controller: decisionCompleted()
deactivate Cleaning

alt 전방 장애물 감지
    Sensor -> Controller: reportFrontObstacleState(frontObstacleDetected=true)
    Controller -> SensorState: updateFrontObstacle(frontObstacleDetected=true)
    Controller -> Cleaning: handleSensorState(SensorState)
    note right of Cleaning: UC-002로 전환
else 먼지 감지
    Sensor -> Controller: reportDustDetected()
    Controller -> SensorState: updateDustDetected(dustDetected=true)
    Controller -> Cleaning: handleDustDetected(SensorState)
    note right of Cleaning: UC-006으로 전환
end

deactivate Controller
@enduml
